* Swipe Controls: Adjust volume/brightness by swiping on player screen.
* Double-Tap Seek: Tap left/right to rewind or skip ahead.
* Auto Toasts: Temporary messages now auto-dismiss after 5s.
* UI Polish: Smoother FAB animation, improved layout in Library.
* Smarter Recents: Short tracks filtered from "Recently Added".
* Link Button: "Open Link" now lives in the top app bar.
